ARTICLE 7.  [OLD]
WAREHOUSE RECEIPTS, BILLS OF LADING
AND OTHER DOCUMENTS OF TITLE
 
     § to 490:7-603  REPEALED.  L 2004, c 163, §34.
 
ARTICLE 7.
DOCUMENTS OF TITLE
 
PART 1.  GENERAL
 
         This article shall be known and may be cited as Uniform Commercial Code  Documents of Title. [L 2004, c 163, pt of §1]
